These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, drama
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, poppy
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | mystery |
| Flower       | amaryllis | poppy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, ivory
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
2. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Color   | black | ivory |
| Birthday      | october     | april  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
City: hamburg, miami
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, february
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| City   | hamburg | miami  |
| Birthday   | july | february |

 #################################

 
