.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-20::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, airplane
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, pall-mall
1. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the game-smoker##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2     |
| Transport   | airplane   | roller |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | game   |

 